{"title":"兵站炊烟","authors":["宫玺"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵站炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫玺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行车高原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪冷风寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见树木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见流泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见村落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见千里路漫漫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落日匆匆下山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没留下晚霞一片；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星儿跳了出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天色渐渐昏暗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由地令人焦急："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜何处宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里避风寒！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必担心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雪线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那颗大星底下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘动着一缕炊烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里是我们的兵站！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里有厚的棉被、热的炕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有清香的茯茶可口的菜饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有革命大家庭的温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一张张热情的笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有来自四面八方的战友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有灯火下有趣的交谈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司机把车开得更快了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直奔白色的炊烟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟象一只亲人的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着我们殷殷招唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心飞了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的身上感到温暖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象走过迢迢千里路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到久别的家园。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}